      <div id="contents" class="app-c-contents-list-with-body">
    
      <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
          
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Members of the public who are involved in legal cases involving the EU should view the public guidance to understand how these cases may be impacted by the end of the Transition Period from 1 January 2021.</p>
</div>
</div>


